text: Mini neighbourhood park with markings on the ground for quick 2.4KM run. Plenty of fitness bars and garden like theme. Children playground available too. And the best part There is a shutter run court as well which is rare in neighbourhood park!

It's a nice little neighbourhood park for exercise and for children to play. The exercise and play areas are quite good. It's less crowded compared to other parks in compassvale. There s a food court and fairprice also nearby. Close to bongank mrt.
Cosy neighbourhood park with children's playground, exercise equipment, and an IPPT training circuit. It has a beautiful willow grove that is just short of a lake to grow around.
The park has a really cool set of bars. Great for body weight exercises like those of Bar Brothers. It's also opposite kopitiam and can be a great place to refuel the body after exercising

A healthy choice to live @ Compassvale Ancilla: PAC  with activites for senior citizens. Ancilla park plus 5 playgrounds for workouts. A coffee shop, 24 hr NTUC,  TOTO booth, a cilinic + misc shops.
Only 3 minutes walk to Baungkok MRT, also the Integrated Grand Residences in near future. The Kopitiam City, NTUC supermarket.
